    local message=$(printf '🤖 *KONFIGURASI GEMINI TTS*

*Status API Key:* %s
*Model:* %s
*Voice:* %s

📝 *Cara Mendapatkan API Key:*
1. Buka https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
